  <summary date="2023-09-18T17:50:38Z" status="Introduced in House">Assault Weapons Excise Act

This bill imposes an additional 1000% excise tax on large capacity ammunition feeding devices and semiautomatic assault weapons. It exempts from such additional tax devices and weapons acquired by the United States or by a state or local government.</summary>
